---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Investment Opportunity - The American Literacy Institute" description="Join us in transforming dyslexia education. Learn about our investment opportunity and financial projections.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Investment Opportunity</h1>
      <p>A compelling opportunity to make a profound social and financial impact</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="executive-summary">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        The American Literacy Institute presents a compelling investment opportunity to address a critical
        and underserved need in the American education landscape. We are launching a K-5 private school
        in Bastrop, Texas, with a proven model for dyslexia education that is both sustainable and scalable.
      </p>
      <div class="summary-grid">
        <div class="summary-card">
          <h3>Initial Enrollment</h3>
          <p class="big-number">36</p>
          <p>Students in Year 1</p>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-card">
          <h3>Annual Tuition</h3>
          <p class="big-number">$15,000</p>
          <p>Per student</p>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-card">
          <h3>Year 1 Revenue</h3>
          <p class="big-number">$720K</p>
          <p>Including ESA funds</p>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-card">
          <h3>Break-Even Point</h3>
          <p class="big-number">34</p>
          <p>Students</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="financial-projections">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Multi-Year Financial Forecast</h2>
      <div class="table-container">
        <table class="financial-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Metric</th>
              <th>Year 1</th>
              <th>Year 2</th>
              <th>Year 3</th>
              <th>Year 4</th>
              <th>Year 5</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Enrollment</strong></td>
              <td>36</td>
              <td>60</td>
              <td>80</td>
              <td>100</td>
              <td>120</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Tuition Revenue</strong></td>
              <td>$540,000</td>
              <td>$900,000</td>
              <td>$1,200,000</td>
              <td>$1,500,000</td>
              <td>$1,800,000</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>ESA Revenue (Projected)</strong></td>
              <td>$180,000</td>
              <td>$300,000</td>
              <td>$400,000</td>
              <td>$500,000</td>
              <td>$600,000</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Total Revenue</strong></td>
              <td>$720,000</td>
              <td>$1,200,000</td>
              <td>$1,600,000</td>
              <td>$2,000,000</td>
              <td>$2,400,000</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Operating Expenses</strong></td>
              <td>$550,000</td>
              <td>$850,000</td>
              <td>$1,100,000</td>
              <td>$1,350,000</td>
              <td>$1,600,000</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="highlight-row">
              <td><strong>Net Operating Income</strong></td>
              <td>$170,000</td>
              <td>$350,000</td>
              <td>$500,000</td>
              <td>$650,000</td>
              <td>$800,000</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="funding-request">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Funding Request</h2>
      <p class="funding-intro">
        We are seeking seed funding of <strong>$250,000</strong> to launch our flagship campus in Bastrop, Texas.
        This investment will provide the foundation for a sustainable and scalable model for dyslexia education.
      </p>
      <div class="funding-breakdown">
        <h3>Use of Funds</h3>
        <div class="funding-grid">
          <div class="funding-item">
            <div class="funding-amount">$100,000</div>
            <div class="funding-label">Facility Build-out & Furnishings</div>
          </div>
          <div class="funding-item">
            <div class="funding-amount">$50,000</div>
            <div class="funding-label">Curriculum & Instructional Materials</div>
          </div>
          <div class="funding-item">
            <div class="funding-amount">$30,000</div>
            <div class="funding-label">Technology & Equipment</div>
          </div>
          <div class="funding-item">
            <div class="funding-amount">$20,000</div>
            <div class="funding-label">Marketing & Enrollment</div>
          </div>
          <div class="funding-item">
            <div class="funding-amount">$50,000</div>
            <div class="funding-label">Working Capital</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="growth-vision">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Growth and Expansion: A National Network</h2>
      <div class="growth-phases">
        <div class="phase-card">
          <h3>Phase 1: The Texas Network (2026-2030)</h3>
          <p>
            After establishing our flagship campus in Bastrop, we will open additional campuses in major
            metropolitan areas including Austin, Houston, and Dallas, leveraging our experience to ensure
            each new campus meets our high standards of academic excellence.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-card">
          <h3>Phase 2: ESA State Expansion (2030-2035)</h3>
          <p>
            Our second phase focuses on states with robust ESA programs, such as Florida, Arizona, and Iowa.
            We will adapt our model to meet specific needs while maintaining our core commitment to
            evidence-based instruction and a faith-friendly culture.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-card">
          <h3>Phase 3: National Leadership & Training (2035+)</h3>
          <p>
            We will establish a National Literacy Training Center in Texas, serving as a hub for innovation
            and excellence in dyslexia education, providing professional development and certification for
            teachers and leaders nationwide.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="impact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Investment Impact</h2>
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Financial Return</h3>
          <p>
            A sustainable business model with projected net operating income of $170,000 in Year 1,
            growing to $800,000 by Year 5.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Social Impact</h3>
          <p>
            Transform the lives of children with dyslexia, building their confidence and equipping
            them for a lifetime of learning and leadership.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Scalable Model</h3>
          <p>
            A proven, replicable model ready for expansion into a national network of schools serving
            thousands of students.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Join Us in This Important Work</h2>
      <p>
        Your investment will not only generate a significant financial return but also a profound social
        impact, helping to unlock the full potential of a generation of students and building a brighter
        future for our country.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn">Contact Us to Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .executive-summary {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .executive-summary h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .summary-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .summary-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .summary-card h3 {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .big-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .financial-projections {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
  }

  .financial-projections h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .table-container {
    overflow-x: auto;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .financial-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .financial-table th,
  .financial-table td {
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bg-color);
  }

  .financial-table thead {
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .financial-table th {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .financial-table tbody tr:hover {
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
  }

  .highlight-row {
    background-color: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .funding-request {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .funding-request h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .funding-intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .funding-breakdown h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .funding-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .funding-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .funding-amount {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .funding-label {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .growth-vision {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
  }

  .growth-vision h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .growth-phases {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .phase-card {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .phase-card h3 {
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .phase-card p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .impact {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .impact h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .impact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .impact-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color) 0%, var(--primary-color) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .impact-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .impact-card p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-color) 0%, #c0392b 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 3rem;
    background-color: var(--white);
    color: var(--accent-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .executive-summary h2,
    .financial-projections h2,
    .funding-request h2,
    .growth-vision h2,
    .impact h2,
    .cta h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .financial-table {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .financial-table th,
    .financial-table td {
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
